<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You don't sound like you mean it at all.</font>

178
00:13:35,052 --> 00:13:37,622
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, even if it doesn't work out,
it's an opportunity.</font>

179
00:13:38,122 --> 00:13:39,023
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Opportunity?</font>

180
00:13:39,123 --> 00:13:40,958
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">An opportunity to find someone else.</font>

181
00:13:42,527 --> 00:13:44,562
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How can you say that?</font>

182
00:13:45,196 --> 00:13:48,766
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ozawa has been
with the same person for 12 years.</font>

183
00:13:48,833 --> 00:13:52,670
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Spending your whole life
with just one person is a waste.</font>

184
00:13:52,770 --> 00:13:54,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The world's full of lovely girls.</font>

185
00:13:55,773 --> 00:13:57,608
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A waste?</font>

186
00:13:59,844 --> 00:14:02,647
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Getting married with your first love</font>

187
00:14:02,980 --> 00:14:04,615
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">is the best thing there is.</font>

188
00:14:07,318 --> 00:14:10,755
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And both of you thinking,
"This person is the one!"</font>

189
00:14:10,822 --> 00:14:13,825
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And promising to stay together.</font>

190
00:14:14,625 --> 00:14:19,497
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And swearing to love each other
in a beautiful chapel.</font>

191
00:14:20,531 --> 00:14:21,766
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's all meaningless.</font>

192
00:14:23,034 --> 00:14:23,868
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Excuse me?</font>

193
00:14:24,335 --> 00:14:26,571
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Promising and swearing. It's meaningless.</font>

194
00:14:26,804 --> 00:14:28,773
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nobody knows
what will happen in the future.</font>

195
00:14:28,973 --> 00:14:32,443
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's more important to enjoy life now.</font>

196
00:14:34,245 --> 00:14:36,547
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you meet someone
you want to be with forever,</font>

197
00:14:36,647 --> 00:14:38,583
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that's the only thing
that can make you happy.</font>

198
00:14:38,683 --> 00:14:43,988
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And if you're both feeling the same,
that's a miracle.</font>

199
00:14:44,055 --> 00:14:46,958
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Everyone is looking for someone like that.</font>

200
00:14:48,860 --> 00:14:52,263
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao. Who have you been talking about?</font>

201
00:14:52,363 --> 00:14:53,197
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

202
00:14:56,067 --> 00:14:58,035
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're so cute when you get upset.</font>

203
00:15:01,038 --> 00:15:03,074
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're the one getting upset, Natsume!</font>

204
00:15:19,423 --> 00:15:23,027
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">UEHARA</font>

205
00:15:25,530 --> 00:15:27,098
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why is Nao like that?</font>

206
00:15:27,932 --> 00:15:28,766
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

207
00:15:29,734 --> 00:15:32,503
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's so quick to take someone's side,
and to get upset.</font>

208
00:15:32,703 --> 00:15:35,706
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's the complete opposite of my type.</font>

209
00:15:37,575 --> 00:15:39,510
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry if she's causing you trouble.</font>

210
00:15:40,111 --> 00:15:41,512
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's a real headache.</font>

211
00:15:42,947 --> 00:15:44,215
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't do anything for her.</font>

212
00:15:45,316 --> 00:15:49,687
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't take her on trips,
and all we eat is her cooking.</font>

213
00:15:51,322 --> 00:15:55,159
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I couldn't do anything
for her birthday either.</font>

214
00:15:56,827 --> 00:15:58,829
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So you wanted to encourage her
in her work at least.</font>

215
00:16:00,731 --> 00:16:02,166
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She wants lots of stuff, too.</font>

216
00:16:03,501 --> 00:16:05,536
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't know if you're her boyfriend
or her guardian.</font>

217
00:16:06,904 --> 00:16:09,907
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What about you?
No interest in getting a girlfriend?</font>

218
00:16:11,142 --> 00:16:11,976
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Me?</font>

219
00:16:12,410 --> 00:16:15,313
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Look, I'll be Natsume
for everyone forever.</font>

220
00:16:21,352 --> 00:16:24,155
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes. I managed to score another date.</font>

221
00:16:24,989 --> 00:16:26,257
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're doing well.</font>

222
00:16:27,792 --> 00:16:30,394
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This looks so good!
Wait. Are you treating me today?</font>

223
00:16:30,695 --> 00:16:31,529
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

224
00:16:36,500 --> 00:16:37,335
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yummy!</font>

225
00:16:40,204 --> 00:16:41,606
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know, you're unusual, too.</font>

226
00:16:41,672 --> 00:16:42,907
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

227
00:16:42,974 --> 00:16:45,443
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No one else would ever ask me
to look after his girlfriend.</font>

228
00:16:46,010 --> 00:16:47,812
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Men are quick to hate me for some reason.</font>

229
00:16:48,546 --> 00:16:49,413
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That is true.</font>

230
00:16:54,585 --> 00:16:56,220
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This may be my first time doing this.</font>

231
00:16:56,921 --> 00:16:57,755
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Doing what?</font>

232
00:16:58,623 --> 00:17:01,392
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Making plans to meet with a male.</font>

233
00:17:02,526 --> 00:17:04,862
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your name is now carved
into the history of my life.</font>

234
00:17:04,929 --> 00:17:06,831
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're making fun of me!</font>

235
00:17:06,897 --> 00:17:09,400
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Best of friends! Amore!
-What are you doing?</font>

236
00:17:09,467 --> 00:17:10,301
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yummy!</font>

237
00:17:11,736 --> 00:17:12,570
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Amore!</font>

238
00:17:12,637 --> 00:17:14,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Stop that. You're such a pain in the ass.</font>

239
00:17:14,972 --> 00:17:15,906
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is there rice?</font>

240
00:17:22,513 --> 00:17:24,382
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao? I was just at Uehara's place...</font>

241
00:17:24,448 --> 00:17:26,083
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Natsume! Meet me right away!</i></font>

242
00:17:27,051 --> 00:17:28,052
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

243
00:17:31,188 --> 00:17:33,457
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume. Here, over here!</font>

244
00:17:33,658 --> 00:17:35,793
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Thank goodness. You're in time.
-What?</font>

245
00:17:37,161 --> 00:17:40,264
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I needed you to see this, Natsume.</font>

246
00:17:43,434 --> 00:17:45,936
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The proposal music box got delivered.</font>

247
00:17:48,305 --> 00:17:49,674
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Kaori.</font>

248
00:17:50,307 --> 00:17:52,076
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know I'm unworthy,</font>

249
00:17:53,411 --> 00:17:57,448
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but will you be with me always?</font>

250
00:18:12,263 --> 00:18:13,164
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

251
00:18:21,138 --> 00:18:24,875
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes!</font>

252
00:18:26,811 --> 00:18:28,179
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So she wanted</font>

253
00:18:28,245 --> 00:18:31,215
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">to be with Ozawa forever, too!</font>

254
00:18:31,882 --> 00:18:35,986
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay. So, you win.</font>

255
00:18:38,622 --> 00:18:42,059
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sure you'll find someone,
too, Natsume.</font>

256
00:18:42,660 --> 00:18:43,494
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

257
00:18:44,095 --> 00:18:46,564
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Someone you'll always want to be with.</font>

258
00:18:56,774 --> 00:18:59,210
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ozawa is crying!</font>

259
00:19:04,482 --> 00:19:05,349
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You want to return it?</font>

260
00:19:06,517 --> 00:19:09,787
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She just didn't want to turn me down
in front of all those people yesterday.</font>

261
00:19:10,654 --> 00:19:13,157
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But she says she can't marry me.</font>

262
00:19:13,891 --> 00:19:15,159
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And this morning she...</font>

263
00:19:16,227 --> 00:19:17,128
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Unbelievable.</font>

264
00:19:17,194 --> 00:19:20,064
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't need the money,
so please let me give it back.</font>

265
00:19:20,698 --> 00:19:23,601
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Every time I look at it, I think of her.</font>

266
00:19:32,710 --> 00:19:33,911
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, that's life.</font>

267
00:19:39,617 --> 00:19:41,385
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello, all!</font>

268
00:19:43,387 --> 00:19:44,455
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Boss!</font>

269
00:19:45,055 --> 00:19:48,859
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ozawa's proposal yesterday was so moving!</font>

270
00:19:49,059 --> 00:19:50,127
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right, Natsume?</font>

271
00:19:50,995 --> 00:19:52,263
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But Nao...</font>

272
00:19:52,329 --> 00:19:53,831
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, it's time for you to work!</font>

273
00:19:54,098 --> 00:19:55,833
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hurry up and get ready.</font>

274
00:19:58,803 --> 00:19:59,970
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you hiding?</font>

275
00:20:00,938 --> 00:20:02,306
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nothing.</font>

276
00:20:02,773 --> 00:20:05,643
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Liar. You're hiding something, aren't you?</font>

277
00:20:06,110 --> 00:20:07,812
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm not.
-You are!</font>

278
00:20:07,878 --> 00:20:09,413
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I said I'm not.
-Show me.</font>

279
00:20:09,680 --> 00:20:12,449
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm not hiding anything.
-Show me. Why are you hiding it?</font>

280
00:20:12,583 --> 00:20:14,251
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao! Look, a bug!</font>

281
00:20:14,318 --> 00:20:16,754
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-A bug?
-That's enough!</font>

282
00:20:45,115 --> 00:20:46,450
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This music box...</font>

283
00:20:47,518 --> 00:20:48,619
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You see, Nao.</font>

284
00:20:48,719 --> 00:20:50,855
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That just happens to be
the same as Ozawa's.</font>

285
00:20:51,021 --> 00:20:53,490
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It's not his music box...
-He returned it.</font>

286
00:20:57,127 --> 00:21:00,297
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He said the proposal
didn't actually go as planned.</font>

287
00:21:02,700 --> 00:21:06,070
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, it's not such a rare thing, really.</font>

288
00:21:18,382 --> 00:21:20,351
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

289
00:21:28,158 --> 00:21:30,661
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm sorry.
-What?</font>

290
00:21:31,495 --> 00:21:33,230
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I made you go through all this trouble.</font>

291
00:21:37,434 --> 00:21:39,169
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, that's right.</font>

292
00:21:39,470 --> 00:21:41,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If I had told you,
you would have never shut up about it.</font>

293
00:21:48,145 --> 00:21:50,281
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes. Thank you.</font>

294
00:22:02,626 --> 00:22:05,829
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Nao. Do you have a minute?</i></font>

295
00:22:09,667 --> 00:22:15,406
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Natsume worries about you, and he's
always secretly watching out for you.</i></font>

296
00:22:15,873 --> 00:22:18,208
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>You're only paying attention to yourself.</i></font>

297
00:22:18,676 --> 00:22:20,577
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>That causes trouble for people.</i></font>

298
00:22:25,115 --> 00:22:28,085
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The coach's training is so harsh.</font>

299
00:22:28,152 --> 00:22:30,921
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Today was rough.
-I can't handle it.</font>

300
00:22:31,922 --> 00:22:33,691
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My shoulders are killing me.</font>

301
00:22:33,757 --> 00:22:36,327
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Who's wants to go grab a bite?
-Me!</font>

302
00:22:36,393 --> 00:22:38,262
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What shall we get?
-All of us?</font>

303
00:22:38,696 --> 00:22:41,398
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Just what is it that's bugging you lately?</i></font>

304
00:22:44,234 --> 00:22:45,703
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you coming too, Nanase?</font>

305
00:22:53,310 --> 00:22:54,945
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've been avoiding me, haven't you?</font>

306
00:22:57,514 --> 00:23:00,784
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.
I was out of line the other day, too.</font>

307
00:23:03,454 --> 00:23:05,456
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No. I...</font>

308
00:23:05,522 --> 00:23:07,791
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You two seem like you can't be bothered!</font>

309
00:23:08,659 --> 00:23:10,828
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You sure you're really not dating?</font>

310
00:23:10,961 --> 00:23:11,895
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Moron!</font>

311
00:23:12,129 --> 00:23:15,165
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nanase and I have a friendship
beyond our genders.</font>

312
00:23:15,399 --> 00:23:16,834
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Forever and always.</font>

313
00:23:25,876 --> 00:23:26,710
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

314
00:23:30,481 --> 00:23:31,548
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

315
00:23:45,429 --> 00:23:46,497
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

316
00:23:46,964 --> 00:23:49,099
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you're going to be late, tell me so!</font>

317
00:23:50,200 --> 00:23:51,902
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I even tried to call
but you didn't pick up.</font>

318
00:23:54,772 --> 00:23:55,606
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

319
00:23:58,776 --> 00:23:59,777
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is something wrong?</font>

320
00:24:01,478 --> 00:24:04,882
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Is something wrong?"
We were supposed to celebrate today.</font>

321
00:24:06,817 --> 00:24:09,119
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I'm so happy right now.</i></font>

322
00:24:09,353 --> 00:24:13,791
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It was like time froze in that moment,
and everyone in the world was blessed.</font>

323
00:24:14,625 --> 00:24:17,494
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll remember it forever.</font>

324
00:24:18,729 --> 00:24:21,732
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! So why don't we celebrate it tonight?</font>

325
00:24:22,533 --> 00:24:25,636
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so sorry. I completely forgot.</font>

326
00:24:27,971 --> 00:24:29,473
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did something happen at work?</font>

327
00:24:34,478 --> 00:24:37,014
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You look completely different
than you did this morning.</font>

328
00:24:41,518 --> 00:24:42,953
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

329
00:24:43,554 --> 00:24:45,289
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There were just some things going on.</font>

330
00:24:47,324 --> 00:24:48,425
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know,</font>

331
00:24:49,927 --> 00:24:51,628
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you don't need to push yourself so hard.</font>

332
00:24:55,032 --> 00:24:57,201
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That fancy shop, and that uniform.</font>

333
00:24:57,968 --> 00:24:59,937
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're obsessed with those things.
You shouldn't be.</font>

334
00:25:02,172 --> 00:25:05,709
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you're not suited for it, you shouldn't
force yourself to stick with it.</font>

335
00:25:12,416 --> 00:25:13,717
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not suited for it?</font>

336
00:25:14,585 --> 00:25:16,453
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can go back to work
at Evening Star Ramen.</font>

337
00:25:16,553 --> 00:25:19,790
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So you think
I'm not suited for it either, Uehara.</font>

338
00:25:20,991 --> 00:25:22,059
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

339
00:25:22,259 --> 00:25:24,394
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What work am I suited for?</font>

340
00:25:25,863 --> 00:25:27,965
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yoshikawa?
-I'm not quitting.</font>

341
00:25:30,134 --> 00:25:32,569
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't know if I'm not suited for it yet.</font>

342
00:25:32,769 --> 00:25:35,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even I can be helpful to people.</font>

343
00:25:37,474 --> 00:25:39,476
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yoshikawa...
-I'm sorry, Uehara.</font>

344
00:25:41,211 --> 00:25:44,448
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to concentrate
on that job for a while.</font>

345
00:26:01,331 --> 00:26:03,433
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao. This one too, please.</font>

346
00:26:03,934 --> 00:26:04,835
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay!</font>

347
00:26:07,704 --> 00:26:10,340
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing?</font>

348
00:26:10,674 --> 00:26:12,109
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

349
00:26:25,022 --> 00:26:26,523
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Welcome.</font>

350
00:26:29,726 --> 00:26:32,462
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nanase, is it about that present?</font>

351
00:26:41,371 --> 00:26:43,540
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll take this please.</font>

352
00:26:45,442 --> 00:26:46,276
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay.</font>

353
00:26:48,612 --> 00:26:51,215
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're finally going to tell him
how you feel.</font>

354
00:26:52,683 --> 00:26:55,152
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I hope this will make him
think of me a little.</font>

355
00:26:57,354 --> 00:26:59,590
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You have my support.</font>

356
00:27:00,490 --> 00:27:04,194
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you're not suited for it, you shouldn't
force yourself to stick with it.</font>

357
00:27:04,261 --> 00:27:07,764
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even I can be helpful to people.</font>

358
00:27:10,734 --> 00:27:14,771
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean, I truly hope
it goes well for you, Nanase.</font>

359
00:27:14,905 --> 00:27:16,540
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And I also think</font>

360
00:27:16,673 --> 00:27:20,077
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that maybe he doesn't want to ruin
his relationship with you,</font>

361
00:27:20,143 --> 00:27:23,013
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">so that's why he's not confessing
his feelings for you even if he wants to.</font>

362
00:27:24,514 --> 00:27:27,017
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And the idea that he loves someone else</font>

363
00:27:27,317 --> 00:27:29,486
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">might all be in your imagination...</font>

364
00:27:29,586 --> 00:27:31,388
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please don't be ridiculous.</font>

365
00:27:33,457 --> 00:27:34,391
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

366
00:27:35,125 --> 00:27:38,929
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't tell me it's all in my imagination.</font>

367
00:27:39,896 --> 00:27:42,599
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You have no idea about our relationship.</font>

368
00:27:43,500 --> 00:27:44,534
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

369
00:27:45,269 --> 00:27:47,704
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just wanted to support you, Nanase...</font>

370
00:27:47,771 --> 00:27:50,040
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's just for your self-satisfaction!</font>

371
00:27:53,110 --> 00:27:54,177
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nanase!</font>

372
00:27:54,444 --> 00:27:58,015
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! Have you still
not finished sorting yet?</font>

373
00:27:59,583 --> 00:28:01,018
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

374
00:28:11,662 --> 00:28:14,464
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Just what is it
that is bugging you lately?</i></font>

375
00:28:19,403 --> 00:28:20,437
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So ugly.</font>

376
00:29:02,112 --> 00:29:04,848
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry about yesterday.</font>

377
00:29:05,949 --> 00:29:08,452
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why would Uehara apologize?</font>

378
00:29:13,490 --> 00:29:15,359
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you, Uehara.</font>

379
00:29:16,927 --> 00:29:17,928
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Yoshikawa.</i></font>

380
00:29:19,029 --> 00:29:22,466
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Remember that time you got so angry
in the gym storage room?</font>

381
00:29:24,301 --> 00:29:27,170
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>You said I wasn't "Poor Uehara."</i></font>

382
00:29:28,739 --> 00:29:30,607
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Back when you didn't like me or anything.</font>

383
00:29:32,776 --> 00:29:35,912
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When they poured water on me.</font>

384
00:29:37,114 --> 00:29:38,949
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When someone is doing his best,</font>

385
00:29:39,516 --> 00:29:42,219
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you should say, "Well done",
not "Poor you", right?</font>

386
00:29:44,388 --> 00:29:47,124
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">For those who don't even know that,</font>

387
00:29:49,059 --> 00:29:51,728
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara won't even express
the slightest interest!</font>

388
00:29:55,665 --> 00:29:56,833
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>At the time, I thought,</i></font>

389
00:29:57,300 --> 00:29:59,403
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"This girl is incredible."</font>

390
00:30:01,805 --> 00:30:05,008
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-Getting so angry for someone else.</font>

391
00:30:07,878 --> 00:30:08,945
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It was only natural...</font>

392
00:30:09,012 --> 00:30:12,749
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No it wasn't. It was not natural at all.</font>

393
00:30:14,818 --> 00:30:16,319
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

394
00:30:18,121 --> 00:30:19,923
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Not to me at least.</i></font>

395
00:30:24,394 --> 00:30:25,228
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>So...</i></font>

396
00:30:28,098 --> 00:30:29,866
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I don't think you're not suited for it.</i></font>

397
00:30:31,635 --> 00:30:32,636
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

398
00:30:33,503 --> 00:30:35,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A job where you strive for others.</font>

399
00:30:36,473 --> 00:30:38,408
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't think you're not suited for that.</font>

400
00:30:48,485 --> 00:30:49,386
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa?</font>

401
00:31:08,905 --> 00:31:09,739
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

402
00:31:21,351 --> 00:31:25,655
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll go apologize to Nanase tomorrow.</font>

403
00:31:26,389 --> 00:31:29,092
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-I totally screwed up today.</font>

404
00:31:32,896 --> 00:31:35,298
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see. Well, do your best.</font>

405
00:31:43,206 --> 00:31:45,141
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I miss you, Uehara.</font>

406
00:31:46,510 --> 00:31:48,578
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're the one who said
we shouldn't meet for a while.</font>

407
00:31:48,678 --> 00:31:50,413
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And I've got my job, too.</font>

408
00:31:51,948 --> 00:31:53,483
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That is true.</font>

409
00:31:54,951 --> 00:31:58,922
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Plus, I could never say
this stuff to your face.</font>

410
00:31:58,989 --> 00:32:01,391
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-Nothing.</font>

411
00:32:04,261 --> 00:32:07,163
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">More importantly,
I'm getting paid tomorrow.</font>

412
00:32:09,132 --> 00:32:10,934
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Shall we go out somewhere for once?</font>

413
00:32:11,368 --> 00:32:14,304
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Go to the kind of place you read about
in a magazine, have a meal.</font>

414
00:32:19,943 --> 00:32:22,812
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm free tomorrow night.</font>

415
00:32:24,614 --> 00:32:25,582
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Good.</font>

416
00:32:36,893 --> 00:32:38,061
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nanase.</font>

417
00:32:43,700 --> 00:32:44,601
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I...</font>

418
00:32:45,769 --> 00:32:47,537
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry about yesterday.</font>

419
00:32:54,077 --> 00:32:58,548
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I didn't think about
the man you like at all.</font>

420
00:32:59,516 --> 00:33:00,817
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just said what I felt like.</font>

421
00:33:02,986 --> 00:33:04,621
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm truly sorry.</font>

422
00:33:08,291 --> 00:33:11,761
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Me, too.</font>

423
00:33:13,897 --> 00:33:14,965
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

424
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:22,172
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I said I was supporting you, Nanase,</font>

425
00:33:22,305 --> 00:33:24,674
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but in the end
I was only thinking about myself.</font>

426
00:33:31,481 --> 00:33:34,517
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But you were thinking about him,
weren't you, Nanase?</font>

427
00:33:35,585 --> 00:33:39,756
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You want to respect his feelings,
and you don't want to trouble him.</font>

428
00:33:42,525 --> 00:33:45,161
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, what I said was irresponsible.</font>

429
00:33:49,866 --> 00:33:51,368
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so sorry.</font>

430
00:34:02,045 --> 00:34:04,481
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please come back to the shop anytime.</font>

431
00:34:25,235 --> 00:34:27,737
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao. We got a last-minute booking
for a party.</font>

432
00:34:27,837 --> 00:34:29,706
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We need to pack flowers, balloons,
and giveaways.</font>

433
00:34:29,773 --> 00:34:31,441
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-<i>Can you come right over?
-What?</i></font>

434
00:34:31,508 --> 00:34:34,444
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have to buy in the flowers by tomorrow.</font>

435
00:34:34,511 --> 00:34:35,345
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Please!</i></font>

436
00:34:35,412 --> 00:34:36,680
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, but...</font>

437
00:34:44,921 --> 00:34:46,256
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">RESEARCH BUILDING NO. 1</font>

438
00:34:59,002 --> 00:35:03,573
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry! I have to work, I'll be late.
I'll be in touch!</font>

439
00:35:05,141 --> 00:35:07,777
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry I kept you waiting!</font>

440
00:35:15,085 --> 00:35:16,586
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry, I'm late...</font>

441
00:35:23,460 --> 00:35:26,730
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're not feeling well.
Please take care of the rest!</font>

442
00:35:27,197 --> 00:35:28,698
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No way.</font>

443
00:35:30,200 --> 00:35:33,970
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This experiment's going nowhere,
I'm starving, and I'm sick of this!</font>

444
00:35:34,938 --> 00:35:37,607
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara, you're still here?</font>

445
00:35:37,741 --> 00:35:39,976
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think I can do some overtime today.</font>

446
00:35:40,043 --> 00:35:43,079
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, I guess your date got canceled.</font>

447
00:35:43,146 --> 00:35:44,948
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And after I paid you in advance
and everything.</font>

448
00:35:45,381 --> 00:35:46,216
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

449
00:35:46,483 --> 00:35:48,952
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She seems to be working hard, too.</font>

450
00:35:52,222 --> 00:35:53,757
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's a special one.</font>

451
00:35:54,090 --> 00:35:56,392
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If your fans hear about this,
they will be furious.</font>

452
00:35:56,726 --> 00:35:58,661
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"She's got Mr. Campus crazy about her!"</font>

453
00:35:58,728 --> 00:36:00,997
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"She should know her place!"
they will say.</font>

454
00:36:02,665 --> 00:36:04,367
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa's an idiot,</font>

455
00:36:05,235 --> 00:36:09,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but when she works hard,
it's always for other people.</font>

456
00:36:11,674 --> 00:36:12,976
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even if it wears her down,</font>

457
00:36:13,343 --> 00:36:17,180
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">she always thinks of other people
rather than herself.</font>

458
00:36:21,851 --> 00:36:25,255
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No one knows that.</font>

459
00:36:30,260 --> 00:36:31,161
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Alright!</font>

460
00:36:55,351 --> 00:36:58,021
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You said you were busy with work, Natsume.
Are you sure about this?</font>

461
00:36:58,087 --> 00:37:01,124
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Seeing your face, Yui,
makes all my fatigue just disappear.</font>

462
00:37:01,224 --> 00:37:03,393
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're always saying stuff like that!</font>

463
00:37:04,227 --> 00:37:06,863
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-So, let me have a good look at that face.
-I'm sure</font>

464
00:37:06,930 --> 00:37:09,199
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao is totally panicking right now.</font>

465
00:37:09,332 --> 00:37:12,435
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-She controls Natsume way too much.
-Right?</font>

466
00:37:12,502 --> 00:37:15,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's going to be a mess
doing that job all by herself...</font>

467
00:37:16,539 --> 00:37:19,409
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What are you talking about?
-Natsume.</font>

468
00:37:20,210 --> 00:37:21,578
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let me in on it.</font>

469
00:37:24,480 --> 00:37:25,748
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is something wrong?</font>

470
00:37:26,416 --> 00:37:27,250
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

471
00:37:27,717 --> 00:37:31,287
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, you haven't said a word in a while.</font>

472
00:37:39,095 --> 00:37:42,699
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao's a strange girl, isn't she?</font>

473
00:37:45,101 --> 00:37:46,369
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What is this all of a sudden?</font>

474
00:37:47,804 --> 00:37:51,507
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's kind of clumsy, kind of direct.</font>

475
00:37:57,780 --> 00:38:01,451
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi, how did you get over her?</font>

476
00:38:03,853 --> 00:38:04,754
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

477
00:38:04,921 --> 00:38:08,892
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now you can talk to her
with a smile on your face.</font>

478
00:38:11,427 --> 00:38:12,262
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

479
00:38:13,263 --> 00:38:14,397
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How come?</font>

480
00:38:20,603 --> 00:38:23,373
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe the same reason I had
when I told her how I feel.</font>

481
00:38:25,742 --> 00:38:28,311
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Because I wanted to be on her side always.</i></font>

482
00:38:31,180 --> 00:38:32,515
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I'm sorry.</i></font>

483
00:38:33,182 --> 00:38:34,717
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I made you go through all this trouble.</font>

484
00:38:38,988 --> 00:38:40,056
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

485
00:38:53,569 --> 00:38:55,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't do it.</font>

486
00:38:55,972 --> 00:38:58,141
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't do this by myself.</font>

487
00:38:59,409 --> 00:39:02,679
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao. It's okay. I'm here now.</font>

488
00:39:07,717 --> 00:39:10,019
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-Milk pudding.</font>

489
00:39:11,054 --> 00:39:13,723
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't eat a bathtub full of it.</font>

490
00:39:14,190 --> 00:39:16,359
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't eat this by myself.</font>

491
00:39:17,427 --> 00:39:19,595
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't do it, Uehara.</font>

492
00:39:19,896 --> 00:39:20,730
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

493
00:39:23,800 --> 00:39:25,935
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Boss! I just finished all the work!</font>

494
00:39:32,842 --> 00:39:35,478
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, it's you, Natsume.</font>

495
00:39:36,312 --> 00:39:38,982
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't "Oh" me! I dumped a date to be here.</font>

496
00:39:44,020 --> 00:39:47,357
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did I...</font>

497
00:39:48,224 --> 00:39:50,460
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did I cause trouble
for you again, Natsume...</font>

498
00:40:20,523 --> 00:40:21,657
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's enough for today.</font>

499
00:40:22,325 --> 00:40:23,159
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

500
00:40:23,359 --> 00:40:24,594
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why don't you go see her?</font>

501
00:40:26,863 --> 00:40:27,897
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your girlfriend.</font>

502
00:40:28,398 --> 00:40:32,869
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Take your eyes off a girl that nice,
and another guy will make a move on her.</font>

503
00:40:35,371 --> 00:40:36,406
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That...</font>

504
00:40:38,441 --> 00:40:39,575
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">won't happen.</font>

505
00:40:44,547 --> 00:40:46,716
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You don't know what the future holds.</font>

506
00:40:47,550 --> 00:40:49,886
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Only you understand her charms, Uehara.</font>

507
00:40:50,319 --> 00:40:51,988
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But what if someone else discovers them?</font>

508
00:40:57,460 --> 00:41:00,163
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I'm the one that's sorry.
I show up and this happens.</i></font>

509
00:41:00,363 --> 00:41:01,697
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

510
00:41:02,932 --> 00:41:04,067
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But...</font>

511
00:41:06,436 --> 00:41:09,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think the work will be fun
with the two of us.</font>

512
00:41:40,336 --> 00:41:41,170
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Listen.</font>

513
00:41:44,040 --> 00:41:46,309
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have an acquaintance who works
at a wedding hall.</font>

514
00:41:47,877 --> 00:41:48,711
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

515
00:41:49,745 --> 00:41:53,349
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Apparently quite a few couples
that get married are first loves.</font>

516
00:41:54,684 --> 00:41:56,619
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't understand it at all, though.</font>

517
00:42:02,758 --> 00:42:04,160
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume.</font>

518
00:42:04,894 --> 00:42:07,296
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What you say and what you do
are two different things.</font>

519
00:42:09,599 --> 00:42:11,501
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What do you mean?
-Nothing.</font>

520
00:42:11,567 --> 00:42:13,202
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just to be clear, I came here</font>

521
00:42:13,302 --> 00:42:15,004
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">because I made a promise to Uehara.</font>

522
00:42:16,439 --> 00:42:17,507
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">To Uehara?</font>

523
00:42:18,708 --> 00:42:21,410
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes. He asked me a favor.</font>

524
00:42:22,445 --> 00:42:24,013
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He said to make sure you were okay.</font>

525
00:42:26,015 --> 00:42:28,618
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He worries even with that blank look
on his face.</font>

526
00:42:33,556 --> 00:42:35,558
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You really act differently
from what you say.</font>

527
00:42:37,793 --> 00:42:38,761
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I...</font>

528
00:42:38,861 --> 00:42:41,964
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You said promises are meaningless.</font>

529
00:42:43,699 --> 00:42:46,269
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But you're keeping your promise to Uehara.</font>

530
00:42:48,771 --> 00:42:50,439
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not so honest, are you?</font>

531
00:42:57,780 --> 00:42:58,614
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

532
00:43:03,819 --> 00:43:07,623
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's not because he asked me to.</font>

533
00:43:14,830 --> 00:43:15,731
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I...</font>

534
00:43:16,432 --> 00:43:17,500
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's his birthday.</font>

535
00:43:18,701 --> 00:43:19,669
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

536
00:43:20,303 --> 00:43:23,973
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's Uehara's birthday next month.</font>

537
00:43:28,644 --> 00:43:29,545
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So,</font>

538
00:43:31,547 --> 00:43:33,883
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I really want to make him happy.</font>

539
00:43:43,025 --> 00:43:46,696
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did you take this job
so you could buy him a present?</font>

540
00:43:53,002 --> 00:43:53,836
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

541
00:44:01,344 --> 00:44:02,445
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara!</font>

542
00:44:03,546 --> 00:44:05,181
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You came to pick me up.</font>

543
00:44:05,348 --> 00:44:06,749
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you still not done?</font>

544
00:44:07,283 --> 00:44:08,751
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm almost done.</font>

545
00:44:08,851 --> 00:44:10,820
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But Natsume is helping me, too.</font>

546
00:44:11,787 --> 00:44:15,291
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No. I think I actually got in the way.</font>

547
00:44:17,493 --> 00:44:19,528
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He made a promise to you, right, Uehara?</font>

548
00:44:23,366 --> 00:44:25,968
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So this is friendship among men.</font>

549
00:44:29,705 --> 00:44:31,040
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come to think of it,</font>

550
00:44:31,140 --> 00:44:33,142
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">he's your first male friend,
isn't he, Uehara?</font>

551
00:44:33,643 --> 00:44:35,578
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What kind of person do you think I am?</font>

552
00:44:35,845 --> 00:44:38,381
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But I've never seen any.
-I've had friends.</font>

553
00:44:42,318 --> 00:44:43,152
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume.</font>

554
00:44:44,387 --> 00:44:45,354
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

555
00:44:51,560 --> 00:44:54,764
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Didn't you know that?
-I didn't.</font>

556
00:44:54,864 --> 00:44:57,767
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-The boy whose family had a restaurant.
-That was Issei!</font>

557
00:44:57,867 --> 00:44:59,235
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've made some recently.</font>

558
00:45:04,874 --> 00:45:06,542
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Abe isn't really my friend.</font>

559
00:45:06,642 --> 00:45:08,210
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's not your friend?</font>

560
00:45:08,978 --> 00:45:10,046
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Amore!</font>

561
00:45:11,480 --> 00:45:12,381
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

562
00:45:13,349 --> 00:45:14,917
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I, Shu Natsume,</font>

563
00:45:15,785 --> 00:45:19,322
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">swear to always and forever be
Shu Natsume no matter what.</font>

564
00:45:20,690 --> 00:45:21,957
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-What?</font>

565
00:45:22,325 --> 00:45:24,927
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What are you talking about?
-Amore?</font>

566
00:45:26,429 --> 00:45:28,230
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Ouch! What?
-That was a close call.</font>

567
00:45:28,864 --> 00:45:29,799
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What was?</font>

568
00:45:30,599 --> 00:45:32,134
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What the hell is this?
-Nothing!</font>

569
00:45:36,105 --> 00:45:39,775
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Once again, we failed to go on a date.</font>

570
00:45:40,576 --> 00:45:43,112
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And you'll probably only invite me</font>

571
00:45:43,212 --> 00:45:45,481
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">to a fancy restaurant
once every ten years.</font>

572
00:45:50,186 --> 00:45:51,954
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you have something else to say?</font>

573
00:45:53,222 --> 00:45:54,056
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

574
00:45:54,623 --> 00:45:55,858
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"I'll be in touch!"</font>

575
00:45:57,560 --> 00:45:59,295
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I kept waiting.</font>

576
00:46:01,897 --> 00:46:03,399
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

577
00:46:11,540 --> 00:46:13,476
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But somehow it makes me feel superior.</font>

578
00:46:15,144 --> 00:46:16,112
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You!</font>

579
00:46:16,212 --> 00:46:19,081
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry! I'll never do it again!</font>

580
00:46:19,148 --> 00:46:21,517
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry! I won't do it again!</font>

581
00:46:22,952 --> 00:46:24,086
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's with you?</font>

582
00:46:24,387 --> 00:46:27,423
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Why are you doing it? Stop that!
-It hurts, doesn't it?</font>

583
00:46:27,490 --> 00:46:29,658
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Why are you doing it?
-Well, you did it to me!</font>

584
00:46:29,725 --> 00:46:30,926
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara...</font>

585
00:46:31,160 --> 00:46:33,095
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Come on.
-Full moon.</font>

586
00:46:33,162 --> 00:46:34,663
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your face looks like a full moon.</font>

587
00:46:34,730 --> 00:46:36,399
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You mean your face.
-No.</font>

588
00:46:50,146 --> 00:46:52,548
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I would like this, please.</font>

589
00:46:58,654 --> 00:47:00,189
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So you decided on this in the end?</font>

590
00:47:01,056 --> 00:47:02,191
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's like you said before.</font>

591
00:47:03,459 --> 00:47:05,661
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What is it that's bugging me?</font>

592
00:47:07,129 --> 00:47:07,963
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

593
00:47:09,532 --> 00:47:11,100
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It was myself.</font>

594
00:47:12,802 --> 00:47:15,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No matter how much we're together,
he doesn't look at me.</font>

595
00:47:16,338 --> 00:47:18,073
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I blamed her,</font>

596
00:47:19,708 --> 00:47:22,945
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and I wanted to tell him how I felt
to make things easier for myself.</font>

597
00:47:25,581 --> 00:47:27,583
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Everything was just about me.</font>

598
00:47:30,519 --> 00:47:32,555
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I hated that side of myself
more than anything.</font>

599
00:47:38,260 --> 00:47:42,965
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But once I acknowledged
that I hated myself,</font>

600
00:47:44,834 --> 00:47:47,703
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I realized that I hated
seeing him troubled even more.</font>

601
00:47:49,939 --> 00:47:51,974
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's better for me to suffer.</font>

602
00:47:55,010 --> 00:47:58,581
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, I'll take that one.</font>

603
00:48:05,855 --> 00:48:08,824
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You don't understand
this kind of stuff, do you?</font>

604
00:48:12,061 --> 00:48:12,995
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes,</font>

605
00:48:20,536 --> 00:48:21,737
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I do.</font>

606
00:48:28,344 --> 00:48:30,246
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The pronunciation
of the accent changes here...</font>

607
00:48:30,346 --> 00:48:32,114
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do you want to have
for dinner tonight?</font>

608
00:48:32,181 --> 00:48:34,250
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Work on this!</font>

609
00:48:34,416 --> 00:48:37,486
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The accents
of the two pronunciations change...</font>

610
00:48:43,125 --> 00:48:45,127
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Didn't you say you wanted
to have croquettes?</font>

611
00:48:45,461 --> 00:48:46,996
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I'm not making any for you.</font>

612
00:48:47,396 --> 00:48:48,864
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why not?</font>

613
00:48:52,668 --> 00:48:53,903
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You do it, Uehara!</font>

614
00:48:54,503 --> 00:48:57,373
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Why do I have to do it?
-Well, I don't know how.</font>

615
00:48:57,473 --> 00:48:59,208
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just try reading it.</font>

616
00:50:37,272 --> 00:50:40,509
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">THIS DRAMA IS FICTIONAL.</font>

617
00:50:40,576 --> 00:50:42,578
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Subtitle translation by
Kumar Sivasubramanian</font>
